import os
import torch
import torch.nn as nn
from torchvision import datasets, models, transforms
from torch.utils.data import DataLoader
from torch.optim import Adam
from torch.optim.lr_scheduler import ReduceLROnPlateau

data_transforms = {
    'train': transforms.Compose([
        transforms.RandomResizedCrop(224),
        transforms.RandomHorizontalFlip(),
        transforms.RandomVerticalFlip(),
        transforms.RandomRotation(40),
        transforms.RandomAffine(degrees=0, translate=(0.2, 0.2)),
        transforms.RandomAffine(degrees=0, shear=0.2),
        transforms.RandomResizedCrop(224, scale=(0.8, 1.2)),
        transforms.ToTensor(),
        transforms.Normalize([0.485, 0.456, 0.406], [0.229, 0.224, 0.225])
    ]),
}

data_dir = "C:/Users/user/Desktop/mandarine/dataset2"
image_datasets = {x: datasets.ImageFolder(os.path.join(data_dir, x), data_transforms[x]) for x in ['train']}
dataloaders = {x: DataLoader(image_datasets[x], batch_size=64, shuffle=True, num_workers=4) for x in ['train']}
dataset_sizes = {x: len(image_datasets[x]) for x in ['train']}

device = torch.device("cuda:0" if torch.cuda.is_available() else "cpu")

model = models.mobilenet_v2(pretrained=True)

# Fine-tuning
for param in model.parameters():
    param.requires_grad = True  # 모든 파라미터를 재학습하도록 설정

num_ftrs = model.classifier[1].in_features
model.classifier[1] = nn.Sequential(
    nn.Dropout(0.5),  # Dropout 추가
    nn.Linear(num_ftrs, 150)
)
model = model.to(device)

criterion = nn.CrossEntropyLoss()
optimizer = Adam(model.parameters(), lr=0.001, weight_decay=0.0001)  # 가중치 감소 적용
exp_lr_scheduler = ReduceLROnPlateau(optimizer, mode='min', factor=0.1, patience=5, verbose=True)

model_save_path = 'C:/Users/user/models/model_best.pth'

# Early stopping
best_acc = 0.0
early_stopping_wait = 0
patience = 10

num_epochs = 20
history = {'train_loss': [], 'train_acc': []}  # history 초기화

for epoch in range(num_epochs):
    for phase in ['train']:
        if phase == 'train':
            model.train()

        running_loss = 0.0
        running_corrects = 0

        for inputs, labels in dataloaders[phase]:
            inputs = inputs.to(device)
            labels = labels.to(device)

            optimizer.zero_grad()

            with torch.set_grad_enabled(phase == 'train'):
                outputs = model(inputs)
                _, preds = torch.max(outputs, 1)
                loss = criterion(outputs, labels)

                if phase == 'train':
                    loss.backward()
                    optimizer.step()

            running_loss += loss.item() * inputs.size(0)
            running_corrects += torch.sum(preds == labels.data)

        epoch_loss = running_loss / dataset_sizes[phase]
        epoch_acc = running_corrects.double() / dataset_sizes[phase]

        print('{} Loss: {:.4f} Acc: {:.4f}'.format(phase, epoch_loss, epoch_acc))

        history[phase+'_loss'].append(epoch_loss)  # 각 에폭의 손실을 history에 추가
        history[phase+'_acc'].append(epoch_acc.item())  # 각 에폭의 정확도를 history에 추가

    exp_lr_scheduler.step(epoch_loss)
    if epoch_acc > best_acc:
        best_acc = epoch_acc
        os.makedirs(os.path.dirname(model_save_path), exist_ok=True)  # 디렉토리 생성
        torch.save(model.state_dict(), model_save_path)
        early_stopping_wait = 0
    else:
        early_stopping_wait += 1
        if early_stopping_wait >= patience:
            print("Early stopping")
            model.load_state_dict(torch.load(model_save_path))

print(f"Best model saved as {model_save_path}")

print("Training loss and accuracy history: ", history)

# 'test' 데이터로더 추가
test_data_transform = transforms.Compose([
    transforms.Resize(256),
    transforms.CenterCrop(224),
    transforms.ToTensor(),
    transforms.Normalize([0.485, 0.456, 0.406], [0.229, 0.224, 0.225])
])

test_dataset = datasets.ImageFolder(os.path.join(data_dir, 'test'), test_data_transform)
test_dataloader = DataLoader(test_dataset, batch_size=64, shuffle=False, num_workers=4)

# 'test' 데이터셋 크기 저장
dataset_sizes['test'] = len(test_dataset)

# Test set에서 모델 평가
model.eval()

test_corrects = 0
test_loss = 0.0

# 'test' 데이터로더 사용
with torch.no_grad():
    for inputs, labels in test_dataloader:
        inputs = inputs.to(device)
        labels = labels.to(device)

        outputs = model(inputs)
        _, preds = torch.max(outputs, 1)

        loss = criterion(outputs, labels)
        test_loss += loss.item() * inputs.size(0)
        test_corrects += torch.sum(preds == labels.data)

# test set의 loss와 accuracy 계산
test_loss = test_loss / dataset_sizes['test']
test_acc = test_corrects.double() / dataset_sizes['test']

# test set의 정확도 출력
print(f'Test Loss: {test_loss:.4f} Test Acc: {test_acc:.4f}')

from PIL import Image
import torchvision.transforms.functional as TF
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

# 테스트 이미지 경로 설정 (사용자가 업로드한 이미지 경로로 수정)
image_paths = [
    "C:/Users/user/Desktop/mandarine/dataset2/train/freshg/istockphoto-182416031-612x612.jpg",
    "C:/Users/user/Desktop/mandarine/dataset2/train/rotteng/22.jpg",
    "C:/Users/user/Desktop/mandarine/dataset2/train/freshg/istockphoto-97752452-612x612.jpg",
    "C:/Users/user/Desktop/mandarine/dataset2/train/rotteng/27.jpg"
    # 추가로 두 개의 이미지 경로를 추가해 주세요.
]

# 예측 및 결과 출력
fig = plt.figure(figsize=(10, 10))

for i, image_path in enumerate(image_paths, 1):
    img = Image.open(image_path)
    img_transformed = test_data_transform(img)  # 이미지에 동일한 전처리 적용
    img_transformed = img_transformed.unsqueeze(0)  # Batch 차원 추가
    img_transformed = img_transformed.to(device)  # GPU로 데이터 이동

    # 예측
    model.eval()  # 평가 모드로 설정
    with torch.no_grad():
        outputs = model(img_transformed)
        _, predicted_class = torch.max(outputs, 1)

    # 클래스 인덱스와 해당 클래스를 딕셔너리로 매핑
    # class_dict의 내용은 실제 데이터셋의 클래스에 맞게 수정이 필요합니다.
    class_dict = {i: class_name for i, class_name in enumerate(test_dataset.classes)}

    # 결과 출력
    print(f"Image {i} 예측:", class_dict[predicted_class.item()])

    # 이미지 출력
    ax = fig.add_subplot(2, 2, i)
    ax.imshow(img)
    ax.set_title(f"Image {i} - Predicted class: {class_dict[predicted_class.item()]}")

plt.tight_layout()
plt.show()
